snippet.title: BE Witches - 2025 Trailer
snippet.description:
Free demo available now!

Battle Monstergirls through a never seen before blend of Match-3 puzzles and Shoot 'em up!
Explore a colorful world with a unique dungeon crawling and Point & click gameplay mix!
Let the titular BE (Breast Expansion) take place and increase your stats and your baps through the power of Amplification!

Support and access public devlogs on PATREON : https://www.patreon.com/nosebecc
Wishlist on STEAM : https://store.steampowered.com/app/1448620/BE_Witches/
Follow on ITCHIO : https://nosebecc.itch.io/b-e-witches

Trailer by Prahbu R : https://www.fiverr.com/virtualmakes/
Footage by @Natetheman223
